c: 11
v: 7
t: "Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin nder balɗe jeegoo, hari arsi Makko kin no ka hoore ndiyam, fii yo O ndaarndo on ko hommbo e mo'on ɓurata moƴƴinnde gollal. Pellet si a wi'i: \"Onon ko on ummintinteeɓe ɓaawo maayde\", maa heeferɓe ɓen wi'u: \"Ɗum wonaali si wanaa mbilewu feeñungu\". @Corrected"